trans-unit.source: Iterates over all preceding sibling nodes according to the <xref href="System.Xml.XPath"></xref> preceding sibling axis rules and returns nodes in reverse document order.
trans-unit.target: Itera em todos os nós irmãos anterior acordo com o <xref href="System.Xml.XPath"> </xref> eixo do irmão anterior regras e retorna nós na ordem inversa de documento.

trans-unit.source: The state of the navigator changes only if the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.PrecedingSiblingIterator.MoveNext%2A> method has returned `true`.
trans-unit.target: O estado do se navegador alterações somente o <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.PrecedingSiblingIterator.MoveNext%2A>método retornou `true`.</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.PrecedingSiblingIterator.MoveNext%2A>

trans-unit.source: The node from which you start traversing the nodes.
trans-unit.target: O nó do qual você inicia atravessando os nós.

trans-unit.source: Enables you to filter nodes based on the name.
trans-unit.target: Permite que você filtre nós com base no nome.
Retorna o navegador de resultados atual.

trans-unit.source: The state of the navigator changes only if the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.PrecedingSiblingIterator.MoveNext%2A> method has returned `true`.
trans-unit.target: O estado do se navegador alterações somente o <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.PrecedingSiblingIterator.MoveNext%2A>método retornou `true`.</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.PrecedingSiblingIterator.MoveNext%2A>

trans-unit.source: Positions the iterator on the next preceding sibling node in the reverse document order.
trans-unit.target: Posiciona o iterador no próximo nó irmão anterior na ordem inversa de documento.

trans-unit.source: If the next preceding node exists, the MoveNext method sets the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.PrecedingSiblingIterator.Current%2A> property to the current result navigator; otherwise, the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.PrecedingSiblingIterator.Current%2A> property remains unchanged.
trans-unit.target: Se o próximo nó anterior existir, o método MoveNext define o <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.PrecedingSiblingIterator.Current%2A>propriedade para o navegador de resultados atual; caso contrário, o <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.PrecedingSiblingIterator.Current%2A>propriedade permanece inalterada.</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.PrecedingSiblingIterator.Current%2A> </xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.PrecedingSiblingIterator.Current%2A>
